items.headline: Penguins at Blue Jackets preview
items.subhead: Marino can tie rookie point streak mark for Pittsburgh defenseman; Columbus eyes fifth win in seven
items.seoTitle: Pittsburgh Penguins Columbus Blue Jackets game preview
items.seoDescription: The Pittsburgh Penguins seek to extend their winning streak to four games and point streak to seven games when they visit the Columbus Blue Jackets at Nationwide Arena on Friday.
items.seoKeywords: Pittsburgh Penguins, at, Columbus Blue Jackets, game preview
items.preview:
PENGUINS (14-7-4) at BLUE JACKETS (10-10-4)

7 p.m. ET; ESPN+, TVAS, FS-O, ATTSN-PT, NHL.TV

 

The Game

The Pittsburgh Penguins seek to extend their winning streak to four games and point streak to seven games when they visit the Columbus Blue Jackets at Nationwide Arena on Friday.

items.headline: Nyquist's hat trick helps Blue Jackets top Penguins
items.subhead: Foligno scores two goals, Korpisalo makes 29 saves for Columbus, which is 5-2-0 in past seven
items.seoTitle: Pittsburgh Penguins Columbus Blue Jackets game recap
items.seoDescription: Gustav Nyquist got his second NHL hat trick, and the Columbus Blue Jackets defeated the Pittsburgh Penguins 5-2 at Nationwide Arena on Friday.
items.seoKeywords: Pittsburgh Penguins, Columbus Blue Jackets, game recap, NHL, hockey, news, Gustav Nyquist, hat trick, Nick Foligno

media.title: Nyquist notches hat trick
media.blurb: PIT@CBJ: Nyquist scores in each period for hat trick
media.description: Gustav Nyquist posted a goal in each period against the Penguins to complete his second career hat trick

items.preview: COLUMBUS -- Gustav Nyquist got his second NHL hat trick, and the Columbus Blue Jackets defeated the Pittsburgh Penguins 5-2 at Nationwide Arena on Friday.
